in front of His Majesty?

8
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:30,760
Yes.

9
00:00:33,110 --> 00:00:34,520
If I hadn't let Wen Zhibai

10
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:36,780
expose himself before Liang's emperor,

11
00:00:37,070 --> 00:00:39,520
how could someone like you,
faking memory loss,

12
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:41,120
walk straight into the trap?

13
00:00:41,610 --> 00:00:42,560
When did you realize

14
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,890
I hadn't lost my memory?

15
00:00:48,470 --> 00:00:49,640
I suspected it

16
00:00:49,950 --> 00:00:51,350
from the very beginning.

17
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:54,280
If you truly forgot,

18
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,360
why would you still keep

19
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,400
my portrait?

20
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,670
You used my love for you

21
00:01:04,790 --> 00:01:05,760
to draw me in.

22
00:01:06,770 --> 00:01:08,230
You played your hand well.

23
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:10,350
I lost, and I admit it.

24
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:21,870
Wen Zhiyuan,

25
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:24,590
this is what you owe me.

26
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:42,920
Where did you hide the imperial seal?

27
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,789
You found out

28
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,310
later than I expected.

29
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,710
You don't have to tell me,

30
00:01:46,810 --> 00:01:48,070
but Song Weiwei's life

31
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,780
might not be spared.

32
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,890
You two were already allied,

33
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:53,640
yet still put on an act.

34
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:07,430
What are you doing?

35
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:14,910
Within palace walls,

36
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:16,840
the most dangerous thing is trust,

37
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:18,770
isn't it?

38
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:20,710
What do you mean?

39
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,710
Wen Zhibai,

40
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,890
you went back on your word.

41
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,910
Torture in the imperial prison
was carried out without restraint.

42
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:35,560
Who knows

43
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,840
how long she can hold out?

44
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,170
Whether she lives or not

45
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,030
is up to you.

46
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:41,280
You broke your word,

47
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:41,980
bullying a defenseless woman,

48
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:43,000
what kind of man does that make you?

49
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,660
Isn't that what you taught me,

50
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,800
Zhiyuan?

51
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,420
What are you doing?

52
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,310
Let me go!

53
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,030
Let me go!

54
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:55,560
Help!

55
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:57,190
Help!

56
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:58,840
Let me go!

57
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:00,240
Let me go!

58
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,080
Let me go!

59
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,430
Help!

60
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,430
Help!

61
00:03:08,970 --> 00:03:10,870
Please, let me go!

62
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,400
Let me go!

63
