I'll talk.

64
00:03:13,470 --> 00:03:14,070
I'll talk.

65
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:15,750
Let her go right now!

66
00:03:17,650 --> 00:03:19,510
The imperial seal is with Yan Chu,

67
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,460
at the villa outside the city.

68
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,890
We're not so different, are we?

69
00:04:05,140 --> 00:04:07,540
You made me
fall for you through deception.

70
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,910
I only wanted you

71
00:04:08,930 --> 00:04:10,530
to feel a fraction of my pain.

72
00:04:13,770 --> 00:04:15,220
[I lost to you.]

73
00:04:25,130 --> 00:04:26,460
Then I'll take my leave.

74
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:51,280
Now it's time to settle what's between us.

75
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,470
Do you really hate me that much?

76
00:04:53,470 --> 00:04:54,520
You destroyed the Chen State,

77
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:56,110
and killed my father and seniors.

78
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:57,510
How could I not hate you?

79
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,750
Everyone I loved

80
00:04:58,750 --> 00:04:59,750
died by your hands.

81
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:01,000
Shouldn't I hate you?

82
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:02,240
Yet you still fell in love

83
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,830
with your father's killer,

84
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,390
didn't you?

85
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:04,870
I never loved you.

86
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,840
You're lying.

87
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,800
I'm not.

88
00:05:07,110 --> 00:05:07,920
Wen Zhiyuan,

89
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,750
today, I, Song Buwei,

90
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,280
am willing to trade my life

91
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:15,310
for the safety of the entire city!

92
00:05:32,140 --> 00:05:33,470
[If you hate me so much,]

93
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:36,830
[then hate me to the end.]

94
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,159
You're right.

95
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,909
I killed your father.

96
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,800
The crown prince of the Chen State

97
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,140
was also killed by my arrow.

98
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:44,120
And your seniors...

99
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,830
-Shut up!
-They all died...

100
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:45,680
by my hand too.

101
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:51,100
When we kissed under the fireworks,

102
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:52,290
did you think of them?

103
00:05:52,290 --> 00:05:53,000
When you lay in my arms,

104
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,820
calling me Zhiyuan,

105
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:54,750
did you think of them?

106
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,020
Admit it, you love me.

107
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:57,600
You're insane!

108
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,659
You won't do it.

109
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,000
You can't kill me!

110
